snippet.title: Foxhole Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Foxhole is a massively multiplayer game where you will work with hundreds of players to shape the outcome of a persistent online war.

Now on Steam Early Access: http://store.steampowered.com/app/505460

Website: www.foxholegame.com

Twitter: https://www.twitch.tv/foxholegame

Discord: discord.gg/foxhole
